OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779883867
OL,3,CSiemens employee left paralysed in
OL,4,C'wholly avoidable' incident at site in
OL,5,CHull
OL,7,FSiemens Gamesa has been fined #600,000
OL,8,Fafter an employee suffered life-
OL,9,Fchanging injuries at a site in Hull.
OL,11,FA 37-year-old woman was left paralysed
OL,12,Ffrom the waist down after the
OL,13,Fstructure she was working on, as part
OL,14,Fof the building of a wind turbine
OL,15,Fblade, collapsed on top of her.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779883867
OL,3,CSiemens employee left paralysed in
OL,4,C'wholly avoidable' incident at site in
OL,5,CHull
OL,7,FThe structure fell after the support
OL,8,Fpoles which had been holding it in
OL,9,Fplace were removed. The section of the
OL,10,Fstructure on which she was working is
OL,11,Fbelieved to have weighed approximately
OL,12,F800kg.
OL,14,FIn a statement, Health and Safety
OL,15,FExecutive (HSE) Inspector Mark Slater
OL,16,Fdescribed the incident as "wholly
OL,17,Favoidable".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779883867
OL,3,CSiemens employee left paralysed in
OL,4,C'wholly avoidable' incident at site in
OL,5,CHull
OL,7,FHe said: "In this case, inadequate
OL,8,Frisk assessment and inadequate systems
OL,9,Fof work left employees to adopt their
OL,10,Fown working methods, exposing them to
OL,11,Fan unacceptable level of risk. This
OL,12,Fwas a wholly avoidable incident."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779883867
OL,3,CSiemens employee left paralysed in
OL,4,C'wholly avoidable' incident at site in
OL,5,CHull
OL,7,FAn investigation by the HSE found that
OL,8,Fthe company had failed to adequately
OL,9,Fassess the risks involved in the work;
OL,10,Fhad failed to devise and implement a
OL,11,Frobust, safe system of work to prevent
OL,12,Femployees from removing the support
OL,13,Fpoles; and had failed to adequately
OL,14,Ftrain employees in safe working
OL,15,Fmethods.
OL,17,FFollowing the incident, the company
OL,18,Fhas introduced a system whereby the
OL,19,Fsupport poles are locked in place and
OL,20,Fcan only be unlocked by a nominated
OL,21,Fperson.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,365,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1779883867
OL,3,CSiemens employee left paralysed in
OL,4,C'wholly avoidable' incident at site in
OL,5,CHull
OL,7,FSiemens Gamesa Renewable Energy Ltd
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to breaching Section
OL,9,F2(1) of the Health and Safety at Work
OL,10,Fetc. Act 1974.
OL,12,FThe company was fined #600,000 and
OL,13,Fordered to pay #7,980.80 in costs at
OL,14,FGrimsby Magistrates' Court on Friday
OL,15,F22 May.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
